          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-sky-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sky-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Full Service Included</h3>
