          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Sensor-activated dispensing, anti-microbial surfaces, and activated oxygen self-cleaning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-7 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-sky-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sky-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Eco-Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Eliminate hundreds of plastic jugs per year. Reduce your carbon footprint by up to 95%.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-2xl p-7 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-sky-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-sky-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Advanced Filtration</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">7-stage purification removes 99.9% of contaminants. NSF certified. Reverse osmosis + remineralization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ COMPARISON TABLE ============ -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-10">Bottleless vs. Bottled Delivery</h2>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-200">
        <table class="w-full border-collapse">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th class="text-left px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-gray-900">Feature</th>
              <th class="text-center px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 bg-gray-50">Bottled Delivery</th>
              <th class="text-center px-6 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white bg-sky-500">PureVida Bottleless</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="text-sm">
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Cost</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">Increases every bottle</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">One flat monthly rate</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Water Supply</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">Limited by deliveries</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">Unlimited, on-demand</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Plastic Waste</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">100s of bottles/year</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">Zero</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Maintenance</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">You handle it</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">PureVida handles it</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Touchless Operation</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">No</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">Yes</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-gray-100"><td class="px-6 py-4 font-medium text-gray-700">Heavy Lifting Required</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-gray-400">40+ lb jugs</td><td class="px-6 py-4 text-center text-sky-500 font-semibold">None</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ BOTTOM CTA ============ -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500 to-sky-600 py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Ready to Stop Managing Your Breakroom?</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-white/85 mb-8">Free 7-day trial. Quick & easy installation. Serving DFW, Austin & San Antonio.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#" onclick="window.scrollTo({top:0,behavior:'smooth'}); return false;" class="inline-block bg-white text-sky-500 font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow cursor-pointer">Start My Free Trial &rarr;</a>
      <a href="tel:+18885340117" class="inline-block border-2 border-white/60 hover:border-white text-white font-bold text-lg px-8 py-4 rounded-xl transition-colors">Call (888) 534-0117</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
  <footer class="bg-gray-900 py-6 px-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs mb-1">&copy; 2026 PureVida Water Technologies. All rights reserved.</p>
    <a href="https://purevidawater.com" class="text-sky-500 hover:text-sky-400 text-xs transition-colors">Return to Main Website</a>
  </footer>

  <!-- ============ SCRIPTS ============ -->
  <script define:vars={{ SUPABASE_URL }}>
    var API = SUPABASE_URL + '/functions/v1';

    // ---- Phone formatting ----
    var phoneInput = document.getElementById('phone');
    phoneInput.addEventListener('input', function(e) {
      var val = e.target.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
      if (val.length > 10) val = val.slice(0, 10);
      if (val.length >= 7) {
        val = '(' + val.slice(0, 3) + ') ' + val.slice(3, 6) + '-' + val.slice(6);
      } else if (val.length >= 4) {
        val = '(' + val.slice(0, 3) + ') ' + val.slice(3);
      } else if (val.length >= 1) {
        val = '(' + val;
      }
      e.target.value = val;
    });

    // ---- Map city to branch ----
    function getBranch(city) {
      if (city === 'Austin') return 'ATX';
      if (city === 'San Antonio') return 'SAN';
      return 'DFW';
    }

    // ---- Form submit ----
    var form = document.getElementById('trial-form');
    var submitBtn = document.getElementById('submit-btn');
    var submitting = false;

    form.addEventListener('submit', async function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      if (submitting) return;
      submitting = true;
      submitBtn.disabled = true;
      submitBtn.textContent = 'Submitting...';

      var cityVal = document.getElementById('city').value;

      var payload = {
        source: 'google_ads',
        form_type: 'contact',
        business_name: document.getElementById('company').value.trim(),
        first_name: document.getElementById('fname').value.trim() || null,
        last_name: document.getElementById('lname').value.trim() || null,
        email: document.getElementById('email').value.trim() || null,
        phone: document.getElementById('phone').value.trim() || null,
        city: cityVal || null,
        branch: getBranch(cityVal),
      };

      try {
        var res = await fetch(API + '/ingest-lead', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(payload),
        });
        var json = await res.json();

        if (json.ok) {
          if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
            gtag('event', 'generate_lead', {
              event_category: 'form',
              event_label: 'google_ads_trial',
              city: cityVal,
            });
          }
          window.location.href = '/free-trial-thank-you';
        } else {
          alert(json.error || 'Something went wrong. Please try again.');
          submitting = false;
          submitBtn.disabled = false;
          submitBtn.innerHTML = 'Claim My Free 7-Day Trial &rarr;';
        }
      } catch (err) {
        alert('Network error. Please check your connection and try again.');
        submitting = false;
        submitBtn.disabled = false;
        submitBtn.innerHTML = 'Claim My Free 7-Day Trial &rarr;';
      }
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
